      <div class="row"><span class="k">GL / cost ledger</span><span class="v" style="color:var(--amber)">● nightly</span></div>
      <div class="row"><span class="k">Access logs</span><span class="v" style="color:var(--ink-4)">○ gap identified</span></div>
